Privacy Policy for the CreativeList Browser Extension

Last Updated: 01.11.2025

Thank you for using the CreativeList browser extension (hereinafter referred to as the "Extension"). We highly value your privacy and take all necessary measures to protect it. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle your data.

1. Data Collection

CreativeList does not collect, store, or transmit your personal data or any other data related to the use of the Extension.

2. Data Usage

Since we do not collect any data, we do not process, use, or share it with third parties.

3. Security

CreativeList is designed with modern security standards and performs its functions locally on your device. All data you work with in the Extension remains solely on your device and is not transmitted to our servers or third-party servers.

4. Changes to the Privacy Policy

We reserve the right to make changes to this Privacy Policy. If changes are made, we will update the last updated date at the beginning of the document. We recommend periodically checking this page for updates.

5. Contact Us

If you have any questions or suggestions regarding this Privacy Policy, please contact us.

Thank you for choosing CreativeList!